headline: UNPACK '26: EXPEDIA, HOTELS.COM, AND VRBO REVEAL HOW TRAVELLERS WILL EXPLORE THE WORLD IN 2026
summary: Today, Expedia Group released Unpack '26: The Trends in Travel™. The annual global report highlights shifts in traveller behaviour and the destinations set to dominate itineraries in 2026, including several Canadian destinations and activities spotlighted throughout.
